urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:i.826#Ladies' Paradise, instead of turning her from it, preserved her quiet
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:i.827#gentle demeanour with a Norman obstinacy. She simply replied: “We shall
