urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:i.858#lace, heightened in its whiteness by the ground glass globes of a row of
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:i.859#gas jets, and against this chapel-like background the ready-made goods
