urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.17#Denise noticed that several of these gentlemen took stock of her in
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.18#passing. This increased her timidity; she felt quite unable to follow
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.19#them, and resolved to wait till they had all entered before going in,
