urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.22#When she returned to the principal entrance, she found a tall young man,
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.23#pale and awkward, who appeared to be waiting as she was.
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.24#“I beg your pardon, mademoiselle,” he finished by stammering out, “but
