urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.304#The manager laughed heartily. “Oh! I don't mind, that will just suit
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.305#me; it will treble the sale, and as my only interest is to attain heavy
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.306#receipts----”
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:ii.307#But Bourdoncle remained very grave, biting his lips. He drew his
