urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.413#keep his looms going, for a loom that stands still is a dead loss. Under
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.414#these circumstances how can you expect that we, with our limited plant,
