urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.886#“Eighty thousand francs!” repeated Bourras. “Why not a hundred thousand
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.887#at once? It's this immense sum of money that makes me indignant Do they
