urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.890#Denise gently observed, in her calm, quiet way: “They'll have it in nine
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.891#years' time, when your lease expires.”
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:vii.892#And, notwithstanding her uncle's presence, she begged of the old man to
