urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:viii.80#opinion.
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:viii.81#“Dear me! you are quite free to support these great hairbrained houses.
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:viii.82#Each one has his ideas, my girl. If you were not disgusted at being so
