urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:viii.109#weighing the portions. The consciousness of his defeat deprived him of
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:viii.110#the confidence he used to have as a respected employer. Pépé thought his
