urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.254#of white socks, one whole room covered with white swanskin, traversed
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.255#in the distance by a stream of light. But the brightness shone with
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.256#especial brilliancy in the central gallery, amidst the ribbons and the
