urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.259#Round the iron columns were twined flounces of white muslin, looped
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.260#up now and again with white silk handkerchiefs. The staircases were
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.261#decorated with white drapings, quiltings and dimities alternating along
