urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.279#“Oh! extraordinary!” repeated the ladies. “Wonderful!”
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.280#They never tired of this song in praise of white that the goods of the
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.281#entire establishment were singing. Mouret had never conceived anything
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.282#more extraordinary; it was the master stroke of his genius for display.
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.283#Beneath the flow of all this whiteness, in the apparent disorder of
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.284#the tissues, fallen as if by chance from the open drawers, there was a
