urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.309#heights. The buzz of voices made a great noise like a rushing stream. Up
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.310#above, the profusion of gildings, the glazed work picked out with gold,
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.311#and the golden roses seemed like a ray of the sun shining on the Alps of
