urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.493#“Keep still, Lucien! Don't you think it's rather tight, mademoiselle?”
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.494# And with the sharp look of a woman difficult to deceive, she examined
