urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.505#The Ladies' Paradise to make some purchases. The young people were
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.506#to accompany Denise to Valognes, a regular marriage trip, a month's
