urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1177#your arm to Madame de Boves, that would be wiser than causing a scandal.
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1178#The deuce! you who professed such scorn before the universal rascality
