urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1188#Blanche rejoined them, and they were soon lost in the crowd. Then
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1189#Mouret, alone and pensive, crossed the shop once more. This scene, which
