urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1191#increased his fever, and decided him to make a supreme effort. A vague
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1192#connection arose in his mind: the robbery by this unfortunate woman,
