urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1198#Six o'clock was about to strike, the daylight decreasing outside was
urn:cts:fuTexts:zola.paradise.novoa:xiv.1199#gradually forsaking the covered galleries, already dark and waning
